    run AddFieldsHandler.
END.

/* _UIB-CODE-BLOCK-END */
&ANALYZE-RESUME


&Scoped-define SELF-NAME b_Helpb
&ANALYZE-SUSPEND _UIB-CODE-BLOCK _CONTROL b_Helpb C-Win
ON CHOOSE OF b_Helpb IN FRAME DEFAULT-FRAME /* Help on Fields */
